title: Study Hall: ENTREPRENEUR STARTS BUSINESS FROM WASTED FOOD
itunes:title: Study Hall: ENTREPRENEUR STARTS BUSINESS FROM WASTED FOOD
description:
In this Study Hall Jasmine Crowe talks about starting Goodr, which is a startup focused on eliminating food waste by recovering surplus food from businesses and redistributing it to people in need. 


Link to full episode: https://youtu.be/WBzz-QjP4uA
